OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FDoctors were not influenced by
OL,8,Fresearch about race when they decided
OL,9,Fto release triple killer Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane about an hour before he
OL,11,Fcaused a woman to jump out of a first
OL,12,Ffloor window, The Nottingham Inquiry
OL,13,Fhas heard.
