OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FFormer mechanical engineering student
OL,8,FCalocane, who has been diagnosed with
OL,9,Fparanoid schizophrenia, repeatedly
OL,10,Fkicked at the door of a property on 24
OL,11,FMay 2020 while he was experiencing
OL,12,Fpsychosis, leading the 22-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman inside to severely damage her
OL,14,Fspine while trying to escape.
OL,16,FThe inquiry previously heard doctors
OL,17,Fhad been "leaning towards" sectioning
OL,18,FCalocane earlier that day after he was
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of criminal
OL,20,Fdamage.
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@ZO]
