OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FBut "the team of professionals
OL,8,Fconsidered the research evidence that
OL,9,Fshows over-representation of young
OL,10,Fblack males in detention", Counsel to
OL,11,Fthe Inquiry Rachel Langdale KC had
OL,12,Fsaid, and he was released back into
OL,13,Fthe community.
OL,26,@oD@EOUrD@YO]
