CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FThree years later in June 2023,
OL,8,FCalocane fatally stabbed
OL,9,Fundergraduates Barnaby Webber and
OL,10,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, who
OL,11,Fwere walking home from a night out,
OL,12,Fand grandfather Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,13,Fattempted to kill three more people
OL,14,Fwith a van in Nottingham.
OL,16,FDr Khuram Malik, a consultant
OL,17,Fpsychiatrist who took part in
OL,18,FCalocane's mental health assessment in
OL,19,Fcustody in May 2020, said he does not
OL,20,Fremember the conversation about race
OL,21,Fresearch happening.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
