OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FHe told the central London inquiry,
OL,8,Fwhich is examining events leading up
OL,9,Fto Calocane's killings, on Tuesday:
OL,10,F"When we are making a decision we do
OL,11,Fthat based on the clinical
OL,12,Fpresentation, so we don't take this
OL,13,Finto account.
OL,15,F"The discussion didn't happen and it
OL,16,Fdidn't influence the decision."
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOUxD@_O]
