OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FConsultant psychiatrist Dr Rahul
OL,8,FGandhi, who assessed Calocane at the
OL,9,Fsame time, was interviewed by
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust last year when it was
OL,12,Fdocumented that he said the mental
OL,13,Fhealth professionals had considered
OL,14,Fthe research into race.
OL,16,F"Colour doesn't come into the picture"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
