CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FDr Gandhi said he does not dispute
OL,8,Fthat he said this during his
OL,9,Finterview, but that he was "trying to
OL,10,Ffill the gaps" because he has no
OL,11,Fmemory of the rationale for the
OL,12,Fdecision to release Calocane.
OL,14,FHe said: "I was just hypothesising `
OL,15,Fwere there any things we thought along
OL,16,Fthese lines at the moment in time?
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@NO]vD@JOU
