CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,F"What I was trying to do was reflect
OL,8,Fon what was the thinking at the time.
OL,9,FAs a doctor, or as a patient, whenever
OL,10,Fwe interact there are cognitive biases
OL,11,Fand sometimes some biases come in the
OL,12,Fway because we are aware of research
OL,13,Fevidence.
OL,15,F"Whatever I'm (saying) here, it's from
OL,16,Fmy notes rather than from my memory of
OL,17,Fthat day."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUyD@JO]
