OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776798669
OL,3,CRace research did not influence
OL,4,Cdecision to release triple killer,
OL,5,Cinquiry told
OL,7,FHe added: "Demographics don't make any
OL,8,Fchange to my practice. Patients are
OL,9,Fadmitted to hospital or discharged
OL,10,Fbased on the severity, risk and need
OL,11,Fof the patient.
OL,13,F"The colour doesn't come into the
OL,14,Fpicture at all."
OL,16,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,17,Fand three counts of attempted murder,
OL,18,Fis detained indefinitely in a high-
OL,19,Fsecurity hospital after prosecutors
OL,20,Faccepted his not guilty pleas to
OL,21,Fmurder.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOUvD@PO]
